ygData.messageBody:
Um high horse? So far the only thing I've seen in my replies were that low
levels never get something new. As for overcrowding it's not at your levels
you just have to be willing to travel a bit or move away from oasis/nro/
lake r/sk bit. In the past two weeks I've played my 50 necro, a shaman
startng at 1 -21, a cleric level 28, and a druid level 37. You know what I
didn't have any problems finding spots except for my necro. So maybe you
just don't know where to hunt.

Naeeldar
